Package: diagnoser
Type: Package
Title: Graphical residual diagnostics and related tools
Version: 0.0.2.3
Author: Robert Schnitman <robertschnitman@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Robert Schnitman <robertschnitman@gmail.com>
Description: Plot residuals, store model results in a data frame, and convert raw text files into word-frequencies data frames.  The diagnose() family provide alternative graphs to Base R's plot(lm()). Additional functions--inspired by the broom library--calculate margin of errors and confidence intervals alongside regression results.
URL: https://github.com/robertschnitman/diagnoser
BugReports: https://github.com/robertschnitman/diagnoser/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.4.2), tm (>= 0.7.0), ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1), gridExtra (>= 2.3), lazyeval (>= 0.2.1), rlang (>= 0.1.4), scales (>= 0.5.0), magrittr (>= 1.5)
License: GNU General Public License v3.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: TRUE
